      },
      "date": "2023-11-19 17:14:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nin general looks OK, but can you please clarify when writeback is used in our case? we don't set it in OSD. iirc, the only way to have it set is partial-page truncate?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "6dc5f1749fe074f271cbc0cce6a6deffc6aa61ac",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 353,
        "name": "Li Dongyang",
        "email": "dongyangli@ddn.com",
        "username": "lidongyang"
      },
      "date": "2023-11-19 23:31:55.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> Patch Set 3:\n> \n> in general looks OK, but can you please clarify when writeback is used in our case? we don't set it in OSD. iirc, the only way to have it set is partial-page truncate?\n\nAlex, this has nothing to do with lustre OSD but triggers a problem when SFA QA is testing exa with fio doing IO directly to the block device.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "c98d2177b506d039f949c7d11c68d4b2f1e38817",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 119,
        "name": "Alex Zhuravlev",
        "email": "bzzz@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "bzzz"
      },
      "date": "2023-11-20 05:53:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\ninteresting.. thus we don't really need this for Lustre? is it used for testing only?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "3a55aac1af1a24bf2a6b2bd1249d84413e476103",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2023-11-20 06:33:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nWell, we need it to be able to test the block device that ldiskfs is layered on (eg. fio or sgpdd-survey or similar). Strictly speaking, the same issue could be hit by mke2fs or e2fsck that do direct block-device access.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "d4b4a4994980aa020beb74c64853494fda4680a9",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 119,
        "name": "Alex Zhuravlev",
        "email": "bzzz@whamcloud.com",
